  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with psoriasis will be evaluated. The investigators will collect personal history,
      concomitant diseases and in particular the presence of type 2 diabetes mellitus, impaired
      fasting glucose and impaired glucose tollerance. The aim of the study will be to evaluate if
      there is a correlation among inflammation, insulin-resistance and psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
